<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Midway's Area 51 infiltrated the top of the arcade charts for 10 months, so it is no surprise that the home version has become popular on the PlayStation. With impressive cinematic effects and stop-motion animation sequences, Area 51 is filled with a generous amount of alien warfare and nonstop action. One or two players can play as soldiers in the elite Strategic Tactical Advanced Alien Response (S.T.A.A.R.) team, which is aiming to stop the spread of an alien-bred lethal infection that has taken over the high security air base at Area 51. 
			<br><br>The S.T.A.A.R. team, which is trained to deal with hostile alien life forms, must survive six extensive stages of gunfire and alien encounters. The sci-fi storyline eventually leads players to covert rooms, government secrets, and cover-ups, and more than a few aliens and UFOs.
			<br><br>Area 51. The infamous high-security military base hidden in the barren Nevada desert and made famous by the blockbuster motion picture Independence Day. It is from here that top-secret research into extra-terrestrial activity is undertaken. Alien craft and creatures examined in the closest detail. Mission : . . . Penetrate Area 51, battle against an alien invasion, destroy the enemy and their spacecraft and save the base from a devastating hostile takeover. Go to it!
                  <br><br>This version of the game comes in a box set which includes a Konami HyperBlaster.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>As a soldier in the elite S.T.A.A.R. Forces, your assignment is to penetrate alien forces at Area 51 and eliminate the threat of the deadly alien infection that has spread throughout the base. Your gear is strapped on, your gun is loaded and now you're ready to clean house. Good Luck!
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>First person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Prerendered graphics</li>
			<li>SCI-FI & Aliens themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

